room_title: Escape room "Captain's Quarters" by Alton Room Escape in St. Louis
room_description:
The year is 1672, and you have booked passage to sail to the New World. Chased by pirates, your ship has run aground. Now you're captured and locked in the Captain's Quarters, and you have 60 minutes to find clues and solve puzzles to escape! Landlubbers and ol' salts alike, work together so your Cap'n isn't made to walk the plank!
There is also a higher difficulty version of the game available. Success rate: 11% (with two clues).
